{"tid":1475403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 文宣好簡單，人人都做到","createTime":"2019-08-15T12:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T12:30:41.000Z","uid":182802,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80bb28298ce5efcbb53ef7f0b71abfff53738769","tid":1475403,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"可能大家都開始攰，愈黎愈少人派傳單／搞放映會<br />\n但文宣唔夠真係會推個運動去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最簡單文宣方法，由而家開始人人都要做：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>１）流動連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebDbGdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebDbGdP.jpg&h=207da648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6sG3pg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6sG3pg.jpg&h=852c63c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSF9sQW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSF9sQW.jpg&h=14d94c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sq0dUvX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSq0dUvX.jpg&h=c7d53301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試諗下，如果一個地鐵車卡同時有２／３個人都係咁，其實都已經幾觸目<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>２）廁格文宣</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1393639/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1393639/page/1</a><br />\n每人印定幾張喺身，屙到邊痴到邊<br />\n安全到不得了，咁都唔知做點對得住所有犧牲／受傷／被捕嘅義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地已經無退路喇<br />\n每人都做多少少啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd86538d51592e9bde7e6604ade821622553a3f3","tid":1475403,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,